              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [],
                  "text": "The Medical Registration (Amendment) Bill (amended MRA) was passed in Parliament in October 2020. The Singapore Medical Council (SMC) and the Ministry of Health (MOH) have since been working with various stakeholders on the transition and operationalisation of the new processes under the amended MRA, for the amended MRA to come into force on 1 July 2022."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [],
                  "text": "A flowchart with an overview of the revised medical disciplinary process is in Appendix 1."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [],
                  "text": "Under the amended MRA, the Minister for Health has appointed a Disciplinary Commission (DC), which will be responsible for appointing and overseeing the procedures and processes of the Disciplinary Tribunals (DTs). The formation of a new DC addresses concerns about the perceived lack of independence of the DTs that are currently appointed by the SMC by ensuring that there is a clear separation of investigation-prosecution and adjudication functions."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [],
                  "text": "The President and Members of the DC appointed on 1 July 2022 are as listed below."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
